# id: IncrementalSSSP -> public static boolean isInSSSP(final Edge<Long, Double> edgeToBeRemoved, DataSet<Edge<Long, Double>> edgesInSSSP) throws Exception
commentText: Function that verifies whether the edge to be removed is part of the SSSP or not._If it is, the src vertex will be invalidated.__@param edgeToBeRemoved_@param edgesInSSSP_@return true or false
codeText: public static boolean isInSSSP(final Edge<Long, Double> edgeToBeRemoved, DataSet<Edge<Long, Double>> edgesInSSSP) throws Exception {__		return edgesInSSSP.filter(new FilterFunction<Edge<Long, Double>>() {_			@Override_			public boolean filter(Edge<Long, Double> edge) throws Exception {_				return edge.equals(edgeToBeRemoved)__			}_		}).count() > 0__	}
